      expl: "Plethora = increased pulmonary blood flow. Left-to-right shunt (VSD) and TGA (mixing with increased flow) → plethoric lungs. (A) TOF and (E) pulmonary stenosis → REDUCED flow (oligaemic lungs). (B) Asthma → hyperinflation, not plethora.",
